---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About - VOLI"
  description="Learn about VOLI's mission to revolutionize volleyball with fantasy leagues, live stats, and community features."
  activePage="about"
>
    <main class="card">
        <h1 class="title">About VOLI</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-label">Our Mission</div>
            <p class="section-text">VOLI LLC is a volleyball technology company building the infrastructure that professional volleyball deserves. We believe volleyball has the talent, the competition, and the fanbase to compete with any major sport — it just needs the right technology ecosystem. We're building a foundation for the sport's digital future.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-label">What We Do</div>
            <p class="section-text">We build products that connect fans more deeply with professional volleyball. From fantasy leagues and real-time statistics to community spaces and interactive games, everything we create is designed to elevate how people experience the sport. Our proprietary AI and deterministic algorithms power detailed analytics — like rotation tracking and play-by-play analysis — that go beyond what's available anywhere else.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-label">Founders</div>
            <div class="founders-grid">
                <div class="founder-card">
                    <img src="/images/founders/ryan.webp" alt="Ryan" class="founder-photo">
                    <strong>Ryan</strong>
                    <span class="founder-role">Founder</span>
                    <p>Ryan works full-time in cybersecurity and software engineering, and built VOLI from the ground up after teaching himself full-stack development to make this happen. He fell in love with volleyball watching his sister play in college, and when she graduated just as the U.S. pro leagues launched, he saw a sport with the talent and fanbase to rival any major league — but missing the digital infrastructure to match. VOLI is his answer: a platform built by a fan who believes pro volleyball deserves it.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="founder-card">
                    <img src="/images/founders/max.webp" alt="Max" class="founder-photo">
                    <strong>Max</strong>
                    <span class="founder-role">Co-Founder</span>
                    <p>Max runs the business and operational side of VOLI, bringing a project management and server administration background from his day job. He and Ryan met in the Air Force a decade ago and have been close friends ever since — despite living on opposite sides of the world, Max even stood in Ryan's wedding — and when the project grew bigger than one person could handle, Max stepped in so Ryan could stay focused on development. He's here because he believes in both the friend and the mission: a sport this good deserves software to match.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-label">Our Products</div>
            <div class="products-grid">
                <a href="/mobileapp" class="product-card">
                    <img src="/images/appicon.webp" alt="" class="product-icon product-icon--rounded">
                    <strong>Voli Mobile App</strong>
                    <span>Fantasy leagues, live stats, community chat, podcasts, and more — all in one app.</span>
                </a>
                <a href="/discordbot" class="product-card">
                    <svg class="product-icon-svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M19.27 5.33C17.94 4.71 16.5 4.26 15 4a.09.09 0 0 0-.07.03c-.18.33-.39.76-.53 1.09a16.09 16.09 0 0 0-4.8 0c-.14-.34-.35-.76-.54-1.09c-.01-.02-.04-.03-.07-.03c-1.5.26-2.93.71-4.27 1.33c-.01 0-.02.01-.03.02c-2.72 4.07-3.47 8.03-3.1 11.95c0 .02.01.04.03.05c1.8 1.32 3.53 2.12 5.24 2.65c.03.01.06 0 .07-.02c.4-.55.76-1.13 1.07-1.74c.02-.04 0-.08-.04-.09c-.57-.22-1.11-.48-1.64-.78c-.04-.02-.04-.08-.01-.11c.11-.08.22-.17.33-.25c.02-.02.05-.02.07-.01c3.44 1.57 7.15 1.57 10.55 0c.02-.01.05-.01.07.01c.11.09.22.17.33.26c.04.03.04.09-.01.11c-.52.31-1.07.56-1.64.78c-.04.01-.05.06-.04.09c.32.61.68 1.19 1.07 1.74c.03.01.06.02.09.01c1.72-.53 3.45-1.33 5.25-2.65c.02-.01.03-.03.03-.05c.44-4.53-.73-8.46-3.1-11.95c-.01-.01-.02-.02-.04-.02zM8.52 14.91c-1.03 0-1.89-.95-1.89-2.12s.84-2.12 1.89-2.12c1.06 0 1.9.96 1.89 2.12c0 1.17-.84 2.12-1.89 2.12zm6.97 0c-1.03 0-1.89-.95-1.89-2.12s.84-2.12 1.89-2.12c1.06 0 1.9.96 1.89 2.12c0 1.17-.83 2.12-1.89 2.12z"/></svg>
                    <strong>Voli Discord Bot</strong>
                    <span>Fantasy leaderboards, live scores, stat leaders, and transaction tracking for Discord servers.</span>
                </a>
                <a href="/redditdailygrid" class="product-card">
                    <svg class="product-icon-svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M12 0A12 12 0 0 0 0 12a12 12 0 0 0 12 12 12 12 0 0 0 12-12A12 12 0 0 0 12 0zm5.01 4.744c.688 0 1.25.561 1.25 1.249a1.25 1.25 0 0 1-2.498.056l-2.597-.547-.8 3.747c1.824.07 3.48.632 4.674 1.488.308-.309.73-.491 1.207-.491.968 0 1.754.786 1.754 1.754 0 .716-.435 1.333-1.01 1.614a3.111 3.111 0 0 1 .042.52c0 2.694-3.13 4.87-7.004 4.87-3.874 0-7.004-2.176-7.004-4.87 0-.183.015-.366.043-.534A1.748 1.748 0 0 1 4.028 12c0-.968.786-1.754 1.754-1.754.463 0 .898.196 1.207.49 1.207-.883 2.878-1.43 4.744-1.487l.885-4.182a.342.342 0 0 1 .14-.197.35.35 0 0 1 .238-.042l2.906.617a1.214 1.214 0 0 1 1.108-.701zM9.25 12C8.561 12 8 12.562 8 13.25c0 .687.561 1.248 1.25 1.248.687 0 1.248-.561 1.248-1.249 0-.688-.561-1.249-1.249-1.249zm5.5 0c-.687 0-1.248.561-1.248 1.249 0 .688.561 1.249 1.249 1.249.688 0 1.249-.561 1.249-1.249 0-.687-.561-1.249-1.25-1.249zm-5.466 3.99a.327.327 0 0 0-.231.094.33.33 0 0 0 0 .463c.842.842 2.484.913 2.961.913.477 0 2.105-.056 2.961-.913a.361.361 0 0 0 .029-.463.33.33 0 0 0-.464 0c-.547.533-1.684.73-2.512.73-.828 0-1.979-.196-2.512-.73a.326.326 0 0 0-.232-.095z"/></svg>
                    <strong>Reddit Daily Grid</strong>
                    <span>A daily volleyball trivia puzzle playable directly inside Reddit.</span>
                </a>
                <a href="/creatorscourt" class="product-card">
                    <img src="/images/icons/creatorscourt.png" alt="" class="product-icon">
                    <div class="product-title-row"><strong>Creators Court</strong><span class="product-badge">Coming Soon</span></div>
                    <span>Analytics, engagement tools, and data APIs for volleyball content creators.</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-label">Independent Platform</div>
            <p class="section-text">VOLI is an independent fan platform created by volleyball fans, for volleyball fans. We're not affiliated with or endorsed by any professional volleyball league or organization. Our goal is to support and celebrate professional volleyball, and we're actively working to build partnerships with leagues and teams.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-label">Data & Statistics</div>
            <p class="section-text">Our products use publicly available statistical data and factual information about professional volleyball games, players, and teams. All statistics, scores, and enhanced analytics are generated from publicly accessible sources using our own technology. We are committed to accuracy and transparency in how we present volleyball data to our community.</p>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    body {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 5rem 2rem 2rem;
        padding-top: calc(5rem + env(safe-area-inset-top));
    }

    .card {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 800px;
        background: var(--bg-card);
        backdrop-filter: blur(40px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(40px);
        border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .card::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--glass-highlight), transparent);
    }

    .title {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .section {
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .section:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .section-label {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .section-text {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .products-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .product-card {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        text-decoration: none;
        text-align: center;
        transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .product-card:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .product-card strong {
        color: var(--text-primary);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .product-card span {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .product-title-row {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .product-badge {
        padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
        border-radius: 100px;
        background: rgba(23, 233, 252, 0.12);
        color: var(--electric-blue);
        font-size: 0.6rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .product-icon {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        object-fit: contain;
    }

    .product-icon--rounded {
        border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .product-icon-svg {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
    }

    .founders-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .founder-card {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .founder-photo {
        width: 96px;
        height: 96px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .founder-photo--placeholder {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--electric-blue));
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: white;
        font-size: 2.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .founder-card strong {
        color: var(--text-primary);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .founder-role {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .founder-card p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        line-height: 1.65;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        body { padding: 6rem 1rem 1rem; }
        .card { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 20px; }
        .title { font-size: 1.5rem; }
        .section-text { font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .products-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .founders-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
</style>
